'''''End of the Eternal Return''''' is an [[Achievement]] in the category ''[[Meetings in Outrealm: Series IV]]''. To complete this achievement, the player needs to defeat the [[Aeonblight Drake]] in [[Co-Op Mode]].

==Gameplay Notes==

==Trivia==
*The achievement's name references {{w|eternal return}}, a philosophical concept popularised by {{w|Friedrich Nietzsche}}, which proposes that time repeats itself in an infinite loop, and all events in the past, present, and future will recur over and over again for all eternity.
